<!--
VOICING PLAN:
- Key C. Different setting from 4143 — more diatonic, G-minor color in middle section.
- Two strophes bars 0-8 with repeat, then through-composed ending bars 9-14.
- Middle section (bars 9-12) uses Bb key area (Db, Eb, Bb chromaticism) for modal darkening.
- RH: 2-note thirds throughout. LH: open voicing 4-note.

VOICE LEADING HIGHLIGHTS:
